Package: frstore
Title: R Wrapper for Cloud Firestore REST API
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("Umair", "Durrani", , "udurrani@presagegroup.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 'frstore' is a convenient way to perform the create, read, update, and delete
    (CRUD) operations on the Cloud Firestore database via REST API.
    It enables R developers to integrate Firebase's Firestore database storage 
    into their projects, particularly in shiny apps.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
